data.description: Nearly 5 Private Acres in Appoquinimink School District is now available for one lucky buyer!  (+/- 2 acres with house is moderately cleared, balance of the property +/- 3 acres is wooded) . Your estate is waiting for you!  Located on nearly 5 level, partially wooded acres just minutes from Middletown, St. Anne's, MOT Charter School and the newly developed Route 301 corridor, this unique home was fully renovated within the past 18 months.   This unique style home has both a traditional and contemporary flair.    In addition to the home, the 37' X 30' outbuilding / garage helps create unlimited potential for this property.  The home has 2 lovely bedrooms on the first floor, plus an adjacent full bath.  It also boasts a great room with cathedral ceiling, massive floor to ceiling fire place, great room concept - open kitchen, living room and eating area with exposed beams.  There is a separate family room that currently serves as a playroom.  A spiral staircase leads to an open loft space, plus the master suite with ensuite master bathroom and walk in closet.  This home is so unique, it can not be fully appreciated without a tour.  The large outbuilding has 2 over-sized garage doors, with enough room for 6 automobiles to be stored or automobiles lifts, plus work and storage room.  There is second floor storage as well.  This 5+ acre lot is a paradise for the anyone who appreciates peace and quiet, outdoor sports, hunting, or just existing in and among nature.  This recently renovated home is being sold "AS IS".    For some lucky buyer, this will be a new estate or farm with a location that is 2nd to none!
